podman-machine-default       ssh://core@127.0.0.1:62128/run/user/501/podman/podman.sock  /Users/vishal/.local/share/containers/podman/machine/machine  true        true
podman-machine-default-root  ssh://root@127.0.0.1:62128/run/podman/podman.sock           /Users/vishal/.local/share/containers/podman/machine/machine  false       true
```
4. I tried the following links independently but none of them seem to work:
- https://medium.com/twodigits/testcontainers-on-podman-a090c348b9d8
- https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=28462495
- https://github.com/testcontainers/testcontainers-java/issues/2088#issuecomment-911586506
- https://github.com/eugene-khyst/podman-testcontainers
- https://tech.durgadas.in/leveraging-testcontainers-with-podman-906ee318a300
- https://stackoverflow.com/questions/71549856/testcontainers-with-podman-in-java-tests/72003620#72003620


